{"tid":881124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高通指蘋果拖欠專利使用費70億美元","createTime":"2018-10-29T08:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T08:00:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fffb9d3492e5c4140cb1afe9b388900b8ffa7f7","tid":881124,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425326-20181029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425326-20181029.htm&d=7329xsprZlMi8AYOta0tnJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=eb66bb79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425326-20181029.htm&h=7151acd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425326-20181029.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國晶片生產商高通指蘋果公司拖欠專利使用費共70億美元。高通在加州一家聯邦法院的聽證會上，指責蘋果存在專利侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果就反駁說，高通試圖強迫公司為同樣的專利支付兩次費用，第一次是當蘋果在iPhone中使用高通晶片的時候，第二次就是以專利使用費名義再次要求收費。<br />\n<br />\n高通重申做法合法，又說多年來蘋果一直認同高通的業務模式。"}]}